title: I Can Copy Talents
description: I Can Copy Talents The young boy Ye Tian gained the ability to replicate the talents of others, this changed his fate from time to time. In order to protect his sister, he struggles to survive in the apocalyptic world when aliens, beasts, and monsters have invaded. In order to to become stronger, he ventures out to the explore the unknown world, gradually finding out the secrets behind the invasion of different dimensions. . . . . . . Other name: Wo Neng Fu Zhi Tian Fu; I Can Copy Talents; I Copy Talents; 我能复制天赋; Talent Copycat; Ability Copy; Thiên Tài Sao Chép; アビリティ・コピー; Your Talent Is Mine
